    <entry>
      <title>偏导数</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/21/Learn/Math/%E5%81%8F%E5%AF%BC%E6%95%B0/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/21/Learn/Math/%E5%81%8F%E5%AF%BC%E6%95%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="定义"><a href="#定义" class="headerlink" title="定义"></a>定义</h1><p>设函数(z=f(x, y))在点$(x_0, y_0)$的某一邻域内有定义, 当(y)固定在(y_0)而(x)在(x_0)处有增量(\Delta x)时, 相应的函数有增量:</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    f(x_0 + \Delta x, y_0) - f(x_0, y_0)</script><p>若极限: </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \lim\limits_{\Delta x \to 0} \frac{f(x_0 + \Delta x, y_0) - f(x_0, y_0)}{\Delta x}</script><p>存在. 则称此极限为函数[z=f(x, y)]在点[(x_0, y_0)]处对[x]的偏导数, 记作:</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \left.\frac{\partial z}{\partial x}\right|_{\substack{x=x_0\\\\y=y_0}} ,    \left.\frac{\partial f}{\partial x}\right|_{\substack{x=x_0\\\\y=y_0}} ,</script><h1 id="意义"><a href="#意义" class="headerlink" title="意义"></a>意义</h1><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \pi</script><h2 id="几何意义"><a href="#几何意义" class="headerlink" title="几何意义"></a>几何意义</h2>]]></content>
      
      
